headline: Jim Cramer Remains Bullish on Vertiv Despite Newer Nvidia Chips
summary: Vertiv Holdings Co (NYSE:VRT) is one of the stocks Jim Cramer talked about, along with market froth. A caller inquired if the company would be impacted as a result of NVIDIA’s newer chips, and Cramer replied: No, my understanding is you’re still going to need Vertiv.
